<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id4d5d1321-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d" identifier="/us/usc/t34/s50111"><num value="50111">§ 50111.</num><heading> Issuance of rules</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Attorney General, after consultation with appropriate members of the law enforcement community and with State and local officials, shall issue rules to carry out this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id4d5d1322-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d">(<ref href="/us/pl/98/473/tII/s609X">Pub. L. 98–473, title II, § 609X</ref>, <date date="1984-10-12">Oct. 12, 1984</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/98/2107">98 Stat. 2107</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id4d5d1323-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id4d5d1324-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="id4d5d1325-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was formerly classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s10512">section 10512 of Title 42</ref>, The Public Health and Welfare, prior to editorial reclassification and renumbering as this section.</p>
</note>
</notes>
